languages.text: The psyker gains +5 {g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerWillpower}Willpower{/g} while under the {g|Encyclopedia:CommonStatusesGlossary}effect{/g} of any allied {g|Encyclopedia:PsykerPowersGlossary}psychic power{/g}, navigator power, or {g|Encyclopedia:Career}doctrine{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Ability}ability{/g}. This {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g} increases by +2 for every other such ability affecting the psyker. If the bonus to Willpower from this {g|Encyclopedia:Talent}talent{/g} is higher than 15, this talent also grants a +1 bonus to {g|Encyclopedia:PsyRating}psy rating{/g}.

traits.locale_text: The Psyker gains +5 Willpower when being under the effect of any allied psychic power, navigator power, or career ability. This bonus increases by +2 for every other such ability affecting the Psyker. If the bonus to Willpower from this talent is higher than 15, this talent also grants a +1 bonus to psy rating.
